title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1220.59 - Vehicles entering terminal required to extinguish headlights
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1220.59 - Vehicles entering terminal required to extinguish headlights

State Regulations

Every driver of a vehicle entering the terminal shall
extinguish the headlights thereof and shall not relight them until leaving the
terminal. Notes
